What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Fatty Acid Diethanolamide Market?

Market Analysis and Insights

Fatty Acid Diethanolamide Market

Data Bridge Market Research analyses that the fatty acid diethanolamide market will witness a CAGR of 5.20% for the forecast period of 2022-2029 and is likely to reach at USD 3,471.87 million by 2029.

Diethanolamides are common components used in cosmetics to act as a frothing agents or as emulsifiers. Chemically, they are amides moulded from diethanolamine and carboxylic acids, typically fatty acids.

The rise in the innovative production technologies and requirement for essential fatty acids in foods and beverages are the major factor accelerating the growth of the fatty acid diethanolamide market in the forecast period of 2022-2029. Furthermore, rise in the demand for functional food, dietary supplements and increase in the number of chronic diseases are also expected to drive the growth of the fatty acid diethanolamide market in the forecast period of 2022-2029. However, variations in the costs of raw materials and genetic effects because of the deficiency of fatty acids like the stroke, inflammation restrains the growth of fatty acid diethanolamide market in the forecast period of 2022-2029, whereas, rising incidence of coronary artery disease and high blood pressure will challenge market growth in the above mentioned forecast period.

In addition, growing awareness among the customers related to the healthy eating and health advantages of essential fatty acids will create ample opportunities for the fatty acid diethanolamide market in the above mentioned forecast period.

